Program: Letter from America by Alistair Cooke
Title: Arab-Israeli peace deal collapses, March 1975
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/b03z8qk7
Last Broadcast Date: Sun 30 Mar 1975
Arab-Israeli peace deal fails. King Faisal shot. Cambodia collapses. Kissinger's diplomatic efforts all end in failure. The sound quality on this recording is variable/poor. This archive edition of Letter from America was recorded by one of two listeners, who between them taped and labelled over 650 Letter From America programmes from 1973 to 1989. It was restored by the BBC in 2014. Show less